name: MBot3D Grid 4 Dual
pre_gcode:
;---------- START GCODE ----------
G21 ; set units to millimeters
G28 ; home all axes
G29 ;Autolevel bed
G1 Z10 F400
G1 X145 Z10 F2400
G92 E0
G1 X145 Z0.5 F400
G1 X120 Z0.5 E20 F360
G92 E0.0
;----------END START GCODE ----------
post_gcode:
M104 S0 ; turn off extruder
M140 S0 ; turn off heatbed
M107 ; turn off fan
G1 Z190 F900
G28 X Y  ;home X Y axes
M84 ; disable motors
